stories.title: Batting tradesmen short in supply at Auckland derby
stories.summary:
Oram celebrates one of his five dismissals in career-best haul  
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
First of all it was Test matches that couldn't go the distance, in terms of time, and now it is One-Day Internationals
